  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Cost: 4 Creation Points </p><p></p><p>This B.I.M can be set on the floor or a flat wall, allowing for it to be placed in a location and triggered remotely.</p><p> This B.I.M takes a bonus action to place and as a part of that action you can make an Intelligence (Stealth) check to hide the B.I.M.</p><p> You may active this B.I.M as a bonus action or a reaction.</p><p> Alternatively, you can spend an action to rig it to automatically explode when a creature enters with 10 feet of the B.I.M.</p><p> When denotated creatures within a 5-foot-radius sphere of the B.I.M must make a Dexterity saving throw dealing 10d4 fire damage on a failed save, or half as much on a successful one.</p><p></p>",
